# Local-only diagnostic + scratch dirs that have caused noisy git status.
# .tmp/ holds dev throwaway scripts (diag_*, time_*, verify_*) — keep them
# locally but never commit. agent/ at the root has been accidentally typed
# multiple times where agents/ was intended; ignoring stops the stray subdir
# from showing up in `git status` again. *.docx at the repo root catches
# stray Word docs uploaded for ad-hoc testing — fixtures should live under
# tests/fixtures/ and skill assets under skills/.
.tmp/
/agent/
/*.docx
